track_notes: The start of this peak is identical to JF-084 Lusk N2. In fact it is as easy to go over Lusk N2 for a double activation, as it is to bypass it on the west side as we did on the way up.
track_title: Lusk from Hwy 68, by north ridge

track_notes: This track will traverse the entire Lusk Ridge, allowing activations on Stony, Lusk N2 and Lusk Peak.  It is probably easiest to do it in that order.  Of all the routes that have been done on these three summits, this track probably incorporates the most efficient of all the routes.
